INSERT INTO `php_html_ln` VALUES (2, 'vn', 'N;', '', '', NULL, '...Our  story', 'With over 20 years experience in jewellery design, Ken Luong established Dallany Jewellery Designs in 1996, with the vision that one-of-a-kind luxury pieces should be affordable and the shopping experience should be memorable.\r\n\r\n“I believe that individuality should be effortless, expresses Ken, that’s why I like to think of my jewellery designs as a method of self-expression in which brings out the wearers’ natural beauty and uniqueness.”\r\n\r\nKen’s one-of-a-kind pieces, ranging from the tastefully simple to the beautifully complex, spring from both Ken’s own distinctive perception of form and his client’s ideas. “Sometimes, a client will come to me with a vision of exactly what it is that they want,” explains Ken, “but other times, I have the opportunity of helping my client uncover their needs, and together we will come up with a design which will truly reflect their personal style.”\r\n\r\nThe result of Ken’s attention to detail and eye for beauty often bring forth artful masterpieces rather than just accessories. The graceful combination of exquisite gemstones and structural forms in Ken’s designs is comparable to perfectly orchestrated music. Ken has mastered his craft to a degree that cannot be surpassed – thus, raising the standard for luxurious jewellery designs, and rightfully claiming the title that Dallany Jewellery Designs is sincerely in ‘a class by itself.’');

